(236, 79, 'Intermediate Level Syllabus', 'Duration: 14 hours | Level: intermediate | Topics: Advanced Formulas: INDEX/MATCH, XLOOKUP, IFERROR | Named Ranges & Dynamic Arrays | Advanced Pivot Tables & Pivot Charts | Power Query: Import & Transform Data | Data Analysis with What-If Tools (Goal Seek, Scenario Manager) | Advanced Conditional Formatting | Array Formulas | Text Functions (LEFT, RIGHT, MID, CONCATENATE) | Working with Multiple Sheets & Workbooks | Introduction to Macros & VBA | Dashboard Design | Intermediate Project: Sales Reporting Dashboard', 2),
