(2337, corp-32, 'Advanced Level Syllabus', 'Duration: 28 hours | Level: advanced | Topics: Metaclasses & Abstract Base Classes | Multithreading, Multiprocessing & AsyncIO | Performance Profiling with cProfile & timeit | Memory Management & Garbage Collection | Building REST APIs with FastAPI/Flask | SQLAlchemy ORM & Advanced DB Patterns | Machine Learning with Scikit-learn | Web Scraping with BeautifulSoup & Scrapy | Packaging & Distribution (PyPI) | Docker for Python Applications | CI/CD with GitHub Actions | Capstone Project: End-to-End ML Pipeline or Web Application', 3);
